      <title>中国经济强国正承受经济放缓的冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-06-11/guangdong-is-feeling-the-brunt-of-china-s-economic-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着四十年来生活水平的提高出现停滞迹象，这个全国最具创业精神的省份面临的痛苦十分严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-06-11/guangdong-is-feeling-the-brunt-of-china-s-economic-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 21:00:23 GMT</pubDate>
